{"tid":2293783,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"五眼聯盟促恢復DQ議員職務","createTime":"2020-11-20T13:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T14:40:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a55d4c794f9f55bbfae038791330a38493d72ac","tid":2293783,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T13:18:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/MNY6FAXRLZCQLO3PWMP7IENOW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FMNY6FAXRLZCQLO3PWMP7IENOW4%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BQomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=6b11aea3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FMNY6FAXRLZCQLO3PWMP7IENOW4%2F&h=eb59c489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/MNY6FAXRLZCQLO3PWMP7IENOW4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n五眼聯盟促恢復DQ議員職務<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e64Bvm2RD7VkER3ErD4y-6YFRQw=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/REBMF2AGWVHXZI4ZXEJFDFFRSA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe64Bvm2RD7VkER3ErD4y-6YFRQw%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FREBMF2AGWVHXZI4ZXEJFDFFRSA.jpg&h=0699d781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■五眼聯盟外長前日發表聯合聲明，對中國取消香港四名民主派立法會議員資格表示極度關切。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n由澳洲、加拿大、新西蘭、英國及美國組成的五眼聯盟外長前日發表聯合聲明，對中國取消香港四名立法會議員資格表示極度關切，並要求中國履行對國際的承諾及對港人的責任，立即讓相關議員復職。<br />\n<br />\n五國外長在聯合聲明重申，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指中國做法明確違反具有法律約束力、在聯合國登記的《中英聯合聲明》下應盡的國際義務，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅：小心眼睛被戳破<br />\n<br />\n五國「籲中國停止破壞港人根據《中英聯合聲明》和《基本法》選出代表的權利。為了香港穩定繁榮，中港當局尊重香港人民表達合理關切和意見的管道極為重要」。五國最後表示，中國身為國際社會的領導成員，盼中國履行國際承諾及對港人的責任，並呼籲中國當局重新考慮針對香港立法會的行動，立即讓相關議員復職。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅昨表示，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港府就五國外長發出的聯合聲明，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"6ede857ecf5ad4fee405ee096e6ebdc286163090","tid":2293783,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:37:43.000Z","msg":"掛成team 公仔俾立會保安撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好咁啦"},{"pid":"693c2267befba9e81c9803b2b711d193fee0b000","tid":2293783,"uid":172223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:40:24.000Z","msg":"唔洗恢復啦 制裁依家議會入面果d就得"}]}